<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>A Special Page</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffe6f0, #e6ccff);
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
    }

    header {
        padding: 60px 20px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
        color: #d63384;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 18px;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border: none;
        background: #d63384;
        color: white;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #a61e66;
    }

    section {
        padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    .card-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        width: 200px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    footer {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    #popup {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 40%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>A Special Tribute 💖</h1>
    <p>
        This page is created to appreciate someone who brings calmness,
        beauty, and positive energy wherever she goes. My Favor my Favorite 😊
    </p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Click for Surprise</button>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>What Makes Her Special ✨</h2>
    <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card">Kind Heart 💕</div>
        <div class="card">Beautiful Mind 🧠</div>
        <div class="card">Calm Spirit 🌸</div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Short Message 💌</h2>
    <p>
        Sometimes people come quietly into our lives, but they leave a
        lasting impact that words cannot fully explain.
    </p>
</section>

<div id="popup">
    <h3>😊 Just So You Know</h3>
    <p>You are appreciated more than you think.</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="hideMessage()">Close</button>
</div>

<footer>
    Made with respect and simplicity ❤️
</footer>

<script>
    function showMessage() {
        document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "block";
    }

    function hideMessage() {
        document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "none";
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
